      <title>美联储官员古尔斯比谈“极佳”就业报告、通胀和利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-on-superb-jobs-report-inflation-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比 (Austan Goolsbee) 对 9 月份美国就业报告表示赞赏。古尔斯比在接受“彭博未平仓合约”节目 Mike McKee 采访时补充说，通胀率可能低于央行 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-on-superb-jobs-report-inflation-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:45:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ADM 在收获季节暂停爱荷华州大豆压榨厂的生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/adm-idles-iowa-soybean-crushing-plant-during-harvest-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在农民收获创纪录作物的时期，阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司将关闭其位于爱荷华州的唯一一家大豆压榨设施数周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/adm-idles-iowa-soybean-crushing-plant-during-harvest-season</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:33:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储古尔斯比称美国 9 月份就业报告“极佳”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-calls-september-us-jobs-report-superb-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比在接受“彭博未平仓合约”节目迈克·麦基采访时谈到9月份美国就业报告时表示：“从现实角度看，你真的不能要求一份更好的经济报告了。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-calls-september-us-jobs-report-superb-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:31:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>代理劳工部长苏表示制造业就业岗位将再次增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/manufacturing-jobs-will-grow-again-su-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理劳工部长朱莉·苏表示，随着企业不断投资，制造业将会增长。她还谈到码头工人重返工作岗位。她说，这证明集体谈判是有效的。苏在“彭博公开市场”节目中谈到了 9 月份的就业报告。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/manufacturing-jobs-will-grow-again-su-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铜冶炼厂警告关闭，紧缩谈判正在进行中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/copper-smelters-warn-of-closures-as-crunch-talks-get-underway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，随着与主要矿商的年度供应谈判开始，铜冶炼厂发出警告称，如果行业加工费大幅下降，工厂可能会关闭甚至停业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/copper-smelters-warn-of-closures-as-crunch-talks-get-underway</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史密斯威森公司墨西哥枪支诉讼案获最高法院复审</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/smith-wesson-gets-us-supreme-court-review-on-mexico-gun-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将考虑驳回墨西哥政府的一项诉讼，该诉讼指控史密斯威森品牌公司和其他枪支制造商为向与该国暴力贩毒集团有关的人员出售枪支提供便利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/smith-wesson-gets-us-supreme-court-review-on-mexico-gun-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 13:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡新任领导人会见国际货币基金组织并完成协议磋商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/sri-lanka-s-new-leader-calls-for-tax-relief-in-first-imf-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡新总统举行了上任以来的首次会见国际货币基金组织官员，并启动了推进该国债务重组的举措，同时确认与该国债券持有人商定的条款与官方债权人协议相当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/sri-lanka-s-new-leader-calls-for-tax-relief-in-first-imf-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 07:32:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>精神航空努力达成救助协议以避免破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/spirit-airlines-creditors-struggle-to-reach-rescue-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，精神航空重组债务、避免申请破产的努力遭遇阻碍，因为经过数月与债券持有人的谈判，该公司未能达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/spirit-airlines-creditors-struggle-to-reach-rescue-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 00:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市缩减涨幅，因交易员消化劳动力数据：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市回吐早前涨幅，因市场担心就业报告强于预期意味着通胀可能比预期更为根深蒂固。就业报告削弱了人们对美国央行下个月再次大幅降息的预期，美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
